targets.rawSql:
SELECT
  $__timeGroupAlias("time",$__interval),
  avg(lat) AS "lat",
  avg(lon) AS "lon"
FROM geo
WHERE
  $__timeFilter("time")
GROUP BY 1
ORDER BY 1

SELECT
  $__timeGroupAlias("time",$__interval),
  avg(lat) AS "lat_recent",
  avg(lon) AS "lon_recent"
FROM geo
GROUP BY 1
ORDER BY 1 desc
LIMIT 1

SELECT
  $__timeGroupAlias("time",1h),
  avg(lat) AS "lat_all",
  avg(lon) AS "lon_all"
FROM geo
GROUP BY 1
ORDER BY 1

SELECT
  $__timeGroupAlias("time",$__interval),
  avg(salinity) AS "salinity",
  avg(temp) AS "temp"
FROM geo
WHERE
  $__timeFilter("time") AND
  salinity >= 20 AND
  salinity <= 38 AND
  temp >= 5 AND
  temp <= 35
GROUP BY 1
ORDER BY 1

SELECT
  $__timeGroupAlias("time",$__interval),

WHERE
  $__timeFilter("time")
GROUP BY 1
ORDER BY 1
